        },
        {
            "title": "長和據悉考慮讓旗下屈臣氏集團上市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，長江和記實業有限公司考慮將旗下健康與美容零售公司<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:屈臣氏集團;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/屈臣氏集團\">屈臣氏集團</a>上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，長和已與財務顧問在商討潛在上市事宜，最早可能明年進行。因涉及非公開討論，知情人士要求匿名。他們表示，屈臣氏集團若在香港上市，或可籌集20億美元或更多資金。其中一位知情人士還透露，也可能考慮在英國進行雙重上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據網站，屈臣氏集團在全球31個市場有17,000多家門店，其中包括英國的Superdrug和德國的Rossmann等連鎖品牌。該集團還在亞洲各地經營著屈臣氏連鎖店，並在香港經營雜貨、洋酒和電子產品門店。新加坡主權財富基金淡馬錫控股持有屈臣氏集團約25%的股份。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-07ce97ba-b220-3084-b03b-2b1ffe54437a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，目前還處於初步考慮階段，尚未做出最終決定，包括潛在發行規模。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長和與淡馬錫的代表均不予置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長和之前就考慮過將屈臣氏集團上市，但始終未能實現。淡馬錫也探索過包括出售其股份等選項。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道瓊周五早些時候報導稱，長和計畫讓屈臣氏集團在香港和英國雙重上市，目標是明年上半年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題CK Hutchison Is Said to Weigh Listing for Health Retailer Watson</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Shirley Zhao.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%92%8C%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%AE%93%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%88%E8%87%A3%E6%B0%8F%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-075021804.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 16:50:57",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國金茂據悉計畫三年多以來首次發行境外債券",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"657\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sCZA6OPYLGx_DYpDGyvG6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2118fbdd5f70a0b58eb6bd629b20c646\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，有國資背景的開發商<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:中國金茂;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/中國金茂\">中國金茂</a>控股集團有限公司計畫三年多以來首次發行境外債券。中國房地產行業近幾年嚴重滑坡，這次發行勢將再次考驗投資者的投資意願。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國金茂在穆迪的評級為垃圾級，中國央企中國中化控股有限責任公司持有其部分股權，並且在各大城市擁有數百個項目。其附屬公司上海金茂投資管理集團有限公司在2023年初曾發行離岸人民幣債券。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對中國金茂債券發行的需求將反映出市場對政府支持房地產行業的觀感。據知情人士透露，中國決策層正在考慮新一輪支持政策以扭轉房地產市場情緒，包括首次在全國範圍內對新增個人住房貸款提供貼息。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d4cf5029-8f07-3c45-8192-383a3ef80397-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"657\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.26ocOfH3yxUi96U2T5CwQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/395769ffdc127a503dd0bf1b3395e73f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士說，金茂計畫發行三年期離岸人民幣債券，即所謂「點心債券」。據彭博匯編的數據，如果成功發行，這將是該公司自2022年3月以來首次發行境外債券。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士說，點心債券的規模和價格指引等細節仍在討論之中，可能會有變動。由於未獲授權談論此事，知情人士要求匿名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞社周五聯繫中國金茂，該公司未立即進行評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Chinese Property Debt to Get Test as Developer Jinmao Plans Bond</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Emma Dong.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%91%E8%8C%82%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8-070420319.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 15:40:57",
